45
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,280
Isn't it annoying?

46
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,480
What do you mean?

47
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,720
Mai.

48
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,360
You're beautiful,

49
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,840
with high emotional intelligence,
great abilities,

50
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,480
and you even know medicine.

51
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,280
You're better than me at everything.

52
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,480
