76
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,160
You keep it for meditation.

77
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,040
I'm feeling better.

78
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,140
Thanks, bye.

79
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:49,040
- Liu Danyang has a crush!
- Mai Jialing, get back here!

80
