86
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:11,000
It's all because of your greed
that this happened.

87
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,800
If everyone in society

88
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,360
walked to extremes like you

89
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,720
and broke the law,

90
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,320
the consequences would be unimaginable.

91
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,680
I hope you can truly repent

92
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,800
and reform

93
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,360
to get out soon.

94
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,560
Can I go see my mom again?

95
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,680
I've been a burden to you.

96
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,400
Now let's talk about

97
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,080
the hostage situation the other day.

98
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,520
Danyang.

99
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:55,600
I remember criminology talked about

100
