193
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,080
I'll go pay.

194
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,920
No.

195
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:10,960
Don't waste money.

196
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,320
I won't wear it.

197
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,400
Doesn't it look good?

198
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,400
I'll pick a few more for you.

199
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,600
No!

200
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,120
Hello, Mom. What's wrong?

201
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,120
Tata.

202
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,200
Coming back this week?

203
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,960
I'll be back tomorrow.

204
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,680
I'm out shopping with a friend.

205
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:34,430
Okay.

206
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,120
What's wrong, Mom?

207
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,040
Is something wrong?

208
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,160
It's nothing serious.

209
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:41,920
I just came to the hospital

210
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,560
to visit a friend.

211
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:45,080
And I saw your dad.

212
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,800
He was still in a hospital gown.

213
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,120
I don't know

214
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,040
what illness he has.

215
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,600
Do you think...

216
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,600
Mom.

217
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,840
I'll be home tomorrow at noon.

218
00:11:52,850 --> 00:11:53,690
Want something to eat?

219
00:11:53,710 --> 00:11:55,160
I'll bring it home for you, okay?

220
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:56,080
Anything's fine.

221
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,600
Go back to your things.

222
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,770
Come back early tomorrow.

223
00:11:58,770 --> 00:11:59,610
Okay.

224
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:09,000
These drugs were all

225
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,400
found in the trash bins.

226
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:12,920
(Binjiang Anti-narcotics Brigade)

227
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:15,400
According to those we arrested,

228
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,880
no one has ever contacted them directly.

229
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:20,480
They just set up meeting spots online,

230
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:22,120
and those spots are random.

231
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,240
Then they use a black plastic bag

232
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,680
to wrap the drugs

233
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:27,320
and leave them in the trash bins.

234
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,680
The composition of this batch

235
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:31,880
is exactly the same as
what we found with Xiahou Xiong.

236
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,800
Even the trafficking methods
are identical.

237
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:36,120
I also believe this batch

238
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:39,880
is the same batch
that Wu took previously.

239
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,440
So if it's Wu,

240
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,240
why has he been active again

241
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,920
after such a long time?

242
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,520
Because the supply is sufficient.

243
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,480
Or maybe

244
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:52,480
he found new sources.

245
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:54,560
It's possible.

246
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:55,800
No way.

247
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,400
I've blocked all his

248
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,600
foreign routes.

249
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:03,920
Is it possible they found someone

250
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,320
who can make the drugs

251
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:08,120
and set up a self-sustaining

252
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:10,120
production chain?

253
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:12,550
Is it possible that

254
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:14,360
Mad Dog is with him?

255
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,000
I think

256
00:13:18,420 --> 00:13:19,480
the one who saved Mad Dog

257
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,600
must be Wu.

258
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,320
The goods are ready.

259
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,560
The purity absolutely reaches

260
00:13:34,560 --> 00:13:35,700
the sample level you gave me.

261
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:43,520
Are the goods prepared?

262
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:45,320
Dove,

263
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:52,640
didn't you give out

264
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,520
a little trial sample?

265
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,920
Wu,

266
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,520
don't you trust me?

267
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,560
How could I not?

268
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,280
Well done.

269
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:15,840
Mad Dog.

270
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,120
His real name is Li Donghan.

271
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,280
Ten years ago, he entered
the Chemistry Department

272
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,680
at Ocean University
with top grades.

273
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:23,080
(Suspect Info: Li Donghan)
His professor mentioned

274
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:25,200
Li Donghan was very talented.

275
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,780
He was supposed to get into
graduate school through recommendation.

276
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,040
But they said

277
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:30,320
he had some personality issues.

278
00:14:30,520 --> 00:14:31,680
While in college,

279
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:34,240
he got into a fight over
a small matter with his roommate

280
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,800
and injured his eye.

281
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:37,680
He was sent to detention,

282
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:39,520
then he fought with another inmate.

283
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:42,000
I think there are some issues with him.

284
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:45,440
According to testimonies
from people close to him

285
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,520
and the information we have,

286
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:50,280
we can confirm that he and Wu

287
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:52,000
are working together.

288
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,240
So,

289
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,760
our immediate priority

290
00:14:55,350 --> 00:14:57,120
is to move quickly

