00:32:14,150 --> 00:32:15,150
Don't worry.

582
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,280
This plan may be extreme,

583
00:32:17,940 --> 00:32:19,560
but when the truth comes out,

584
00:32:19,840 --> 00:32:21,850
they'll thank you for it.

585
00:32:22,520 --> 00:32:23,440
Trust me.

586
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:31,800
Hey,

587
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:33,080
aren't we going that way?

588
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:34,720
Too many cameras
on the main road.

589
00:32:34,850 --> 00:32:35,760
It's not safe.

590
00:32:58,180 --> 00:32:59,080
Hello.

591
00:32:59,080 --> 00:33:00,920
This is the 110 emergency hotline.

592
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:05,960
Hello?

593
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,240
Can you hear me?

594
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:08,360
Hello?

595
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,400
Calling the police?

596
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,400
Hello?

597
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:12,920
Please speak.

598
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:14,960
Is it

599
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:17,080
inconvenient to talk?

600
00:33:17,190 --> 00:33:18,960
Captain Ye, Chen Lin

601
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:19,840
called us.

602
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,040
But no one spoke.

603
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,200
Put me through.

604
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,880
Track the location of the call.

605
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:25,500
Yes, tracking now.

606
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:30,920
Chen Lin,

607
00:33:31,040 --> 00:33:32,920
this is Ye Zhen, captain
of Hummer Commandos.

608
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,200
Are you safe?

609
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:40,560
Lower your voice!

610
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,600
I will kill you.

611
00:33:42,840 --> 00:33:43,760
Don't scream.

612
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:45,600
Don't scream.

613
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:53,080
I know you can't talk right now.

614
00:33:53,080 --> 00:33:53,980
Don't panic.

615
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:55,920
I'll ask the questions now.

616
00:33:56,040 --> 00:33:57,120
If you can hear me,

617
00:33:57,550 --> 00:33:58,910
just press any key.

618
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:03,960
Good.

619
00:34:04,320 --> 00:34:05,590
Is the call safe?

620
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:08,120
If yes, press once.

621
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:09,360
If not,

622
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:10,310
don't press.

623
00:34:13,350 --> 00:34:14,620
Are you Chen Lin?

624
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:19,840
You're not hurt, right?

625
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:27,470
There are two suspects?

626
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:35,860
What are you hiding?

627
00:34:36,030 --> 00:34:37,240
What exactly are you hiding?

628
00:34:37,240 --> 00:34:38,920
Get away, get away.

629
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,760
- Don't move.
- What is it?

630
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:45,520
Hey,

631
00:34:45,680 --> 00:34:47,420
they called the police, the police!

632
00:34:48,640 --> 00:34:50,040
Throw the phone away, hurry.

633
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:50,960
You...

634
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,230
You...

635
00:34:55,240 --> 00:34:56,600
Behave!

636
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:58,920
You two want to die?

637
00:34:59,080 --> 00:35:00,240
What should we do?

638
00:35:05,720 --> 00:35:07,640
Captain Ye, the phone's
no longer moving.

639
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,320
Can you track the location?

640
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:11,560
It's on the county road
in Hedong Town, Baiyun Village.

641
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:13,040
(Hexi Town, Hedong Town)
Location will be sent.

642
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:14,080
Okay, thanks.

643
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:19,080
Captain, we've learned something.

644
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:21,360
Xu Zheng's family is very average.

645
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:23,320
But Chen Lin's mother is very rich.

646
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:25,000
Her father passed away early.

647
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:27,160
Chen Lin's mother has been living abroad

648
00:35:27,160 --> 00:35:28,600
and running a company.

649
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,400
When they got married,

650
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:32,480
Chen's mother strongly
opposed her marrying Xu Zheng

651
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:35,400
because Xu's family was poor.

652
00:35:35,830 --> 00:35:36,960
In a fit of anger,

653
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,760
Chen Lin severed ties with her mother.

654
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:40,190
They've been apart
for over a decade.

655
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:42,400
Who else knows

656
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:44,000
Chen Lin's mother is very rich?

657
00:35:44,120 --> 00:35:45,360
We asked Xu Zheng,

658
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,400
but he said

659
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,760
he and Chen Lin never talk about

660
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:48,680
her parents.

661
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:50,520
Even Xu Zifeng doesn't know

662
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:51,880
who her grandmother is.

663
00:35:58,460 --> 00:36:03,340
(Policewoman's Mini-Class)

664
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:05,100
(Policewoman's Mini-Class)
Officer, I get a query.

665
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:07,020
Why do you sound the alarm

666
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:08,420
every time you respond to a call?

667
00:36:08,420 --> 00:36:10,180
Don't you worry about
the criminals escaping?

668
00:36:10,220 --> 00:36:11,420
We don't always sound the alarm

669
00:36:11,420 --> 00:36:12,460
when responding to calls.

670
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:14,020
But when it's a major case,

671
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:15,740
we won't hesitate to sound the alarm.

672
00:36:15,740 --> 00:36:17,980
The goal is to deter the criminals.

673
00:36:18,860 --> 00:36:21,580
But what if the criminals escape?

674
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:25,320
Preventing the crime is more important
than capturing the criminals.

675
00:36:33,711 --> 00:36:38,561
♪Wear a smile to hide sorrow♪

